OUR PHOTOSHOOT PROCESS

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

  • I meet you at a chosen location or you come to our studio.
  • When you show up we discuss what you want for your headshot, and review any sample photographs online.
  • We will periodically review pictures on camera (or iPad) to make sure you are getting the images you want.
  • At the end of the headshot session I will send you a link to download all raw high resolution digital headshots for you to view (usually the same day). You can send the link to friends, agents, and family to get their opinion on which headshots you should choose.
  • Email me with the image number of the headshot(s) you want retouched.
  • I will email you a retouched proof for you to approve. Once approved I will upload the headshot(s) to a server and send you a link to download.

LINKEDIN PHOTOGRAPHY IN TORONTO

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

To be taken serious in today’s work environment, you need a professional photograph that works for you and not against you. Yes, your LinkedIn profile is full of accomplishments, with testimonials touting your sheer prowess and awesomeness, but it’s also important that you draw the right attention to your image.

In today’s corporate world, much of the networking we do is online. That’s why personal branding is more important than ever and why a high-quality photograph is your first meeting with the public. We have helped hundreds of CEOs, Senior Executives, Entrepreneurs, Real Estate Agents, Accountants, Actors, Politicians present the professional image they need to be successful. You can find our portraits on many Wikipedia pages, Real Estate Signs, store signage, About Us sections on many top Fortune 500 company’s websites, book covers of famous writers, and startups of some young, successful Entrepreneurs. We know what you need and are more than capable of delivering it in a most professional form. Invest in yourself, as it could be the most profitable small investment you’ve ever made.
